short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A chrome extension to enhance your meet calls

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Unconventional Meet is the open-source, free chrome extension that allows you to enhance your meetings experiences.

Currently in version 0.0.1, it has the following features: 

- Asking for confirmation before closing Google Meet's tab during a call
- Click on the extension icon to focus Google Meet's tab
- Auto-join the meeting instead of landing in the waiting room

Link to the repo https://github.com/giacomocerquone/unconventional-meet
